WEBVTT

00:03.805 --> 00:05.773
Whoa. What's with the cast?
I sprained my wrist.

00:06.007 --> 00:07.107
Oh, no!
What happened?

00:07.142 --> 00:08.809
Don't worry about it.
I'm fine.

00:08.843 --> 00:09.977
Yeah! Geez, Amy.

00:10.011 --> 00:11.011
<i>Back off.</i>

00:11.045 --> 00:12.279
Leave the guy alone.

00:12.280 --> 00:13.560
All right, huddle up, everybody.

00:13.581 --> 00:14.815
<i>Bring it in, bring it in!</i>

00:14.816 --> 00:16.149
<i>So he wouldn't say what happened,</i>

00:16.184 --> 00:17.651
which can only mean one thing.

00:17.685 --> 00:19.920
- He's in a fight club.
<i>- No.</i>

00:19.954 --> 00:22.856
He did it doing something he's
embarrassed by, like smiling.

00:22.857 --> 00:24.358
Only question is, how do you
hurt your arm smiling?

00:24.359 --> 00:25.659
<i>Could be a sports injury.</i>

00:25.693 --> 00:28.295
I sprained my wrist in college
playing field hockey.

00:28.296 --> 00:30.764
Men's field hockey?
Yeah.

00:30.799 --> 00:32.499
It's much more violent
than the women's game.

00:32.500 --> 00:35.102
We're not allowed to wear anything
that protects our breasts.

00:35.103 --> 00:36.804
Attention, everyone,
I can hear you speculating

00:36.838 --> 00:39.807
about the nature and origin
of my injury from my office.

00:39.808 --> 00:42.609
I tripped over an uneven sidewalk.

00:42.610 --> 00:44.578
<i>I did not think
it was relevant to your jobs,</i>

00:44.579 --> 00:48.115
the jobs which you should all
be doing right now.

00:48.116 --> 00:49.716
<i>Get to work.</i>

00:52.520 --> 00:55.555
Do you wanna know
how I actually hurt my wrist?

00:55.590 --> 00:57.390
Yes.

00:57.391 --> 00:59.059
I was hula-hooping.

00:59.060 --> 01:02.395
Kevin and I attend a class
for fitness and for fun.

01:02.396 --> 01:03.430
Oh, my God.

01:03.431 --> 01:05.399
I've mastered all the moves.

01:05.433 --> 01:07.534
The pizza toss...

01:07.535 --> 01:08.702
The tornado...

01:08.703 --> 01:11.938
The scorpion, the oopsie doodle.

01:11.973 --> 01:15.208
Why are you telling me this?

01:15.209 --> 01:18.378
Because no one...
Will ever believe you.

01:18.379 --> 01:20.080
<i>No. No!</i>

01:23.117 --> 01:25.419
You sick son of a bitch.

01:25.420 --> 01:29.140
Sync & corrections by <font color="#00ff00">Rafael UPD</font>
<font color="#ffff00">web dl sync snarry</font>

01:31.000 --> 01:37.074
